      "content": "but why do i have to keep trying if it's just a loop? like, if someone's engine is fundamentally cracked, telling them to keep driving isn't helpful, it's just cruel. sometimes it feels like the most honest thing to do is just accept that the damage is permanent and stop fighting a losing battle. isn't there such a thing as just being beyond repair?",
